<node CREATED="1719502337238" ID="ID_1728102078" MODIFIED="1722038702601" TEXT="# Documenting Existing Code: &#xa;&#x9;**1. Code Analysis**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Utilize AI-powered code analysis tools**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Generate initial documentation**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;3. Include function signatures, data structures, comments I&#xa;&#x9;**2. Documentation Review**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Collaborate with subject matter experts and developers**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Review and enhance generated documentation**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;3. Ensure accuracy and completeness II&#xa;&#x9;**3. Documentation Standards**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Establish documentation standards**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Ensure consistency in formatting, language, and detail &#xa;&#x9;**4. Knowledge Extraction**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Leverage AI-based knowledge extraction techniques**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Capture implicit knowledge from experienced developers**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;3. Enrich documentation &#xa;&#x9;**5. Documentation Management**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Implement centralized documentation management system**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Enable version control, collaboration, and easy access V&#xa;&#x9;**6. Continuous Documentation**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Integrate documentation processes into development lifecycle**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Ensure documentation remains up-to-date">
<attribute NAME="type" VALUE="explanation"/>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1708457272483" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_177367098" MODIFIED="1727740785127" TEXT="**Refactoring Code in a Well-Structured Fashion**">
<font BOLD="true" NAME="Ubuntu Condensed" SIZE="14"/>
<attribute NAME="type" VALUE="expander"/>
<attribute NAME="params" VALUE="4"/>
<attribute NAME="url" VALUE="assets/images/COBOLagency_process_Claude.md"/>
<node CREATED="1719502337238" ID="ID_1306647184" MODIFIED="1722038718226" TEXT="# Refactoring Code in a Well-Structured Fashion: &#xa;&#x9;**1. Code Analysis**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Comprehensive analysis of existing codebase**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Identify areas for refactoring, technical debt, and bottlenecks**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;3. Leverage AI-assisted code analysis tools I&#xa;&#x9;**2. Refactoring Strategy**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Develop refactoring strategy based on analysis**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Prioritize areas for immediate attention**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;3. Define roadmap for incremental refactoring II&#xa;&#x9;**3. Automated Refactoring**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Leverage AI-powered refactoring tools**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Automate tedious and error-prone tasks**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;3. Ensure code quality and adherence to standards &#xa;&#x9;**4. Manual Refactoring**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Employ skilled developers for complex scenarios**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Leverage AI-assisted coding and code review &#xa;&#x9;**5. Testing and Validation**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Implement comprehensive testing strategies**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Regression testing**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;3. Validate functionality and performance V&#xa;&#x9;**6. Continuous Integration and Delivery**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;1. Integrate refactored code into CI/CD pipeline**&#xa;&#x9;&#x9;2. Automated testing, building, and deployment">
<attribute NAME="type" VALUE="explanation"/>
</node>
</node>
