<node CREATED="1727733939582" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_90395881" MODIFIED="1729537538778" TEXT="**DOCUMENT &amp; ANALIZE**">
<font BOLD="true" NAME="IBM Plex Sans Cond" SIZE="16"/>
<attribute NAME="type" VALUE="expander"/>
<node CREATED="1728410724753" ID="ID_167793933" MODIFIED="1729527479859" TEXT="### FEATURES&#xa;&#xa;#### **ORGANIZATION DESCRIPTION**&#xa;* **Strategy**&#xa;* **Processes: BPMN &amp; OKR&#x2019;s**&#xa;&#xa;#### RESOURCES DESCRIPTION&#xa;* **Operational Environment &amp; Ecosystem**&#xa;* **Software Licenses &amp; Versions**&#xa;* **Mainframe**&#xa;* **Network**&#xa;* **Code _ Process Relationship**&#xa;* **Relevance**&#xa;* **Code Specs &amp; Description**&#xa;* **Biz Impact**&#xa;* **Mainframe Environment**&#xa;* **Human Factor**&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;##### **DATA**&#xa;&#xa;*  **MODULES FLOW**&#xa;*  **BIZ IMPACT**&#xa;*  **ANALITICS**&#xa;&#xa;##### **INTERACTIVE DIAGRAMS**&#xa;&#xa;### BENEFITS&#xa;* **Comprehensive documentation preserves mission critical COBOL knowledge.**&#xa;* **Streamlines maintenance and reduces downtime.**&#xa;* **Captures system details to ensure smooth modernization and troubleshooting.**&#xa;* **Empowers teams to manage and upgrade legacy systems confidently.**&#xa;&#xa;##### [Read More](https://cobolagency.com/solutions/document-analize/)&#xa;">
<attribute NAME="type" VALUE="explanation"/>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1727734206159" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1245161368" MODIFIED="1729537535718" TEXT="**OPTIMIZE &amp; REFACTOR**">
<font BOLD="true" NAME="IBM Plex Sans Cond" SIZE="16"/>
<attribute NAME="type" VALUE="expander"/>
<node CREATED="1728410724753" ID="ID_120290247" MODIFIED="1729526867721" TEXT="### PURPOSE&#xa;##### **RELATED ELEMENTS**&#xa;  *  **DATASETS**&#xa;  *  **COPYBOOKS**&#xa;  *  **COBOL**&#xa;  *  **JCL**&#xa;  *  **CICS**&#xa;  *  **DB2**&#xa;&#xa;##### **DATA**&#xa;&#xa;*  **MODULES FLOW**&#xa;*  **BIZ IMPACT**&#xa;*  **ANALITICS**&#xa;&#xa;##### **INTERACTIVE DIAGRAMS**&#xa;&#xa;### **BENEFITS**&#xa;* **Optimization and analysis are essential for enhancing COBOL systems, pinpointing inefficiencies, and refining code for maximum performance.**&#xa;* **Analyzing core functions increases processing speed, reduces resource consumption, and extends the system&#x2019;s lifespan.**&#xa;* **This approach not only improves reliability but also sets a solid foundation for future scalability and integration.**&#xa;&#xa;##### [READ MORE](https://cobolagency.com/solutions/optimize-refactor/)">
<attribute NAME="type" VALUE="explanation"/>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1727734490381" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1748049045" MODIFIED="1729537532546" TEXT="**CODE &amp; DEVELOP**">
<font BOLD="true" NAME="IBM Plex Sans Cond" SIZE="16"/>
<attribute NAME="type" VALUE="expander"/>
<node CREATED="1728410724753" ID="ID_1109402872" MODIFIED="1729527206727" TEXT="### FEATURES&#xa;&#xa;###### Cognitive Representation&#xa;&#xa;* Reverse Engineered Business Concepts&#xa;*  Code Untanglement&#xa;* Code Representation as Business Functions&#xa;&#xa;##### Knowledge Repository&#xa;&#xa;* Business concepts for all ouputs&#xa;* Hierarchical relationships&#xa;##### LLMs&#xa;* Explanation of business concepts&#xa;&#xa;##### REFACTORING&#xa;&#xa;##### RECCOMENDATIONS&#xa;&#xa;#####  **FastAPI Based**&#xa;&#xa;*  **AI BRIDGE**&#xa;     * Python&#xa;     * Rust&#xa;     * HuggingFace&#xa;     * Groq&#xa;     * Cerebras&#xa;&#xa;##### **DATA**&#xa;&#xa;*  **MODULES FLOW**&#xa;*  **BIZ IMPACT**&#xa;*  **ANALITICS**&#xa;&#xa;##### [IBM Modernization](https://www.ibm.com/mainframe-application-modernization)&#xa;&#xa;### **BENEFITS**&#xa;* **COBOL development focuses on adding new functionalities to legacy systems, ensuring they continue to meet evolving business needs and comply with new laws or guidelines from the government, suppliers, or vendors.**&#xa;* **This approach helps by adding new lines of code to have newer functionalities while preserving existing capabilities.**&#xa;* **Ultimately, it enhances the value of legacy systems by making them more adaptable and responsive to future demands.**&#xa;&#xa;##### [READ MORE](https://cobolagency.com/solutions/optimize-refactor/)&#xa;&#xa;">
<attribute NAME="type" VALUE="explanation"/>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1727734608258" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1837360588" MODIFIED="1729537542464" TEXT="**DEBUG &amp; MAINTAIN**">
