<attribute NAME="type" VALUE="expander"/>
<node CREATED="1728410724753" ID="ID_886038443" MODIFIED="1729527125572" TEXT="### FEATURES&#xa;&#xa;### **BENEFITS**&#xa;&#xa;* **Integrate COBOL systems with modern technologies to ensure seamless data flow and enhanced platform communication.**&#xa;* **Encapsulate legacy functionalities within updated IT frameworks, allowing for improved operational agility and compatibility.**&#xa;* **Support future scalability by embedding COBOL systems into a flexible, resilient, and sustainable infrastructure.**&#xa;&#xa;##### [READ MORE](https://cobolagency.com/solutions/optimize-refactor/)&#xa;">
