<node CREATED="1727976015190" ID="ID_1652468026" MODIFIED="1728508274512" TEXT="##### SBOT&#xa;* Low code software, designed to automate complete business flows, &#x201c;End to End&#x201d;, and automate software testing, in different environments: legacy (AS400), web, mobile, API, databases and queues.&#xa;&#xa;##### SBOT AND RPA&#xa;* Fast, effective and economical automation.&#xa;* Converts manual, long and complex processes into automated and reusable processes, which are executed in minutes.&#xa;* Simple programming.&#xa;* Does not require specialized technical knowledge.&#xa;* Allows autonomy in programming.&#xa;* Attended or unattended execution.&#xa;&#xa;##### Powerful Testing&#xa;* Comprehensive and updated approach to testing&#xa;* Testing&#xa;* Agile practices and timely quality&#xa;* Systemic qualities (ISO25000) and risks.&#xa;* Test levels and automation pyramid.&#xa;* Process and product quality&#xa;* Find and correct defects 80% faster.&#xa;* More comprehensive testing with greater coverage.&#xa;&#xa;##### Training&#xa;* Pre-designed or specific courses.&#xa;* Professional instructors.&#xa;* In-person, online or combined training.&#xa;* Consulting&#xa;&#xa;##### Optimization of testing processes.&#xa;* Evaluation and improvement of the software process.&#xa;&#xa;##### Benefits&#xa;* Increase process speed.&#xa;* Improve Time to Market.&#xa;* Reduce reprocessing and operating costs.&#xa;* Increase the quality of solutions.&#xa;* Decouple people from the process.&#xa;* Achieve code reuse and self-service.&#xa;* Reduce dependence on expert knowledge.">
