t;:** {&#xa;      &quot;metrics&quot;:** [&#xa;        &quot;Performance metrics&quot;&#xa;      ]&#xa;    }&#xa;  }&#xa;}&#xa;```&#xa;#### Software Creation Workflow Metrics&#xa;&#xa;* ##### Performance metrics&#xa;```json&#xa;{&#xa;  &quot;key&quot;:** &quot;Performance metrics&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;metrics&quot;:** [&#xa;    &quot;CPU usage&quot;,&#xa;    &quot;Memory usage&quot;,&#xa;    &quot;Response time&quot;&#xa;  ]&#xa;}&#xa;```&#xa;&#xa;* ##### Workplane metrics&#xa;```json&#xa;{&#xa;  &quot;key&quot;:** &quot;Workplane metrics&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;metrics&quot;:** [&#xa;    &quot;Development time&quot;,&#xa;    &quot;Testing time&quot;&#xa;  ]&#xa;}&#xa;```&#xa;">
