<node CREATED="1728658310113" ID="ID_1435962202" MODIFIED="1728662574494" TEXT="#### Generic Software Creation Workflow Templates&#xa;&#xa;* ##### Software Creation Workflows&#xa;```json&#xa;{&#xa;  &quot;name&quot;:** &quot;Software Creation Workflow&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;phase1&quot;:** {&#xa;    &quot;evaluate_problem_drivers&quot;:** true,&#xa;    &quot;develop_workflows&quot;:** true,&#xa;    &quot;iterate_and_refine&quot;:** true,&#xa;    &quot;implement_and_deploy&quot;:** true,&#xa;    &quot;monitor_and_evaluate&quot;:** true&#xa;  },&#xa;  &quot;phase2&quot;:** {&#xa;    &quot;workflows&quot;:** [&#xa;      {&#xa;        &quot;templateName&quot;:** &quot;Workflow Template 1&quot;,&#xa;        &quot;workflows&quot;:** [&#xa;          {&#xa;            &quot;step1&quot;:** {&#xa;              &quot;description&quot;:** &quot;Planning step&quot;&#xa;            },&#xa;            &quot;step2&quot;:** {&#xa;              &quot;description&quot;:** &quot;Design step&quot;&#xa;            },&#xa;            &quot;step3&quot;:** {&#xa;              &quot;description&quot;:** &quot;Development step&quot;&#xa;            },&#xa;            &quot;step4&quot;:** {&#xa;              &quot;description&quot;:** &quot;Testing step&quot;&#xa;            },&#xa;            &quot;step5&quot;:** {&#xa;              &quot;description&quot;:** &quot;Deployment step&quot;&#xa;            }&#xa;          }&#xa;        ]&#xa;      }&#xa;    ],&#xa;    &quot;iterate_and_refine&quot;:** {&#xa;      &quot;iterations&quot;:** [&#xa;        {&#xa;          &quot;iterationNumber&quot;:** 1,&#xa;          &quot;workflow&quot;:** &quot;Workflow Template 1&quot;&#xa;        },&#xa;        {&#xa;          &quot;iterationNumber&quot;:** 2,&#xa;          &quot;workflow&quot;:** &quot;Workflow Template 2&quot;&#xa;        }&#xa;      ]&#xa;    },&#xa;    &quot;implement_and_deploy&quot;:** {&#xa;      &quot;plan&quot;:** &quot;Deployment plan&quot;&#xa;    },&#xa;    &quot;monitor_and_evaluate&quot;:** {&#xa;      &quot;metrics&quot;:** [&#xa;        &quot;Performance metrics&quot;&#xa;      ]&#xa;    }&#xa;  }&#xa;}&#xa;```&#xa;#### Software Creation Workflow Metrics&#xa;&#xa;* ##### Performance metrics&#xa;```json&#xa;{&#xa;  &quot;key&quot;:** &quot;Performance metrics&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;metrics&quot;:** [&#xa;    &quot;CPU usage&quot;,&#xa;    &quot;Memory usage&quot;,&#xa;    &quot;Response time&quot;&#xa;  ]&#xa;}&#xa;```&#xa;&#xa;* ##### Workplane metrics&#xa;```json&#xa;{&#xa;  &quot;key&quot;:** &quot;Workplane metrics&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;metrics&quot;:** [&#xa;    &quot;Development time&quot;,&#xa;    &quot;Testing time&quot;&#xa;  ]&#xa;}&#xa;```&#xa;">
